/**
 *   Nano/Atmega328 PINS: connect LCD to D5 (D/C), D4 (CS), D3 (RES), D11(DIN), D13(CLK)
 *   Attiny SPI PINS:     connect LCD to D4 (D/C), GND (CS), D3 (RES), D1(DIN), D2(CLK)
 *   ESP8266: connect LCD to D1(D/C), D2(CS), RX(RES), D7(DIN), D5(CLK)
 */

